divs: Sighting DetailsMy nephew was working in Unionville MI, He does construction all over the state of MI, He saw what looked to be 2 moons fused. He then snapped a photo and uploaded it to his facebook while at work. I am his aunt and think it needs to be reported. I am including the photo of what he saw, maybe someone else saw this. he has the original photo on his cell phone.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Unionville
This sighting has never been favorited.
Summary: My nephew was working, looked up and saw odd lights.
